    <SupplProvision AmendLawId="412312" AmendLawNum="平成一二年六月七日政令第三一二号" Extract="true" Id="3d0760e2-d3b9-11e9-ab6a-005056b30d52" Type="Amend">
      <SupplProvisionLabel>附　則</SupplProvisionLabel>
      <Paragraph Hide="false" Num="1" OldStyle="false">
